@baseURL = https://<your-tailscale-machine-name>.ts.net/api/v1

### Get All Products
GET {{baseURL}}/products
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get All Products (with filters)
GET {{baseURL}}/products?category_id=1&supplier_id=1&name=Notebook&is_active=1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Get Product by ID
GET {{baseURL}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>

### Create Product
POST {{baseURL}}/products
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "item_code": "NEW-001",
    "name": "New Product",
    "description": "A new product",
    "supplier_id": 1,
    "category_id": 1,
    "unit_cost": 12.50,
    "selling_price": 15.00,
    "is_vat_exempt": 0
}

### Update Product (PUT)
PUT {{baseURL}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "item_code": "UPD-001",
  "name": "Updated Product",
  "description": "An updated product",
  "supplier_id": 1,
  "category_id": 1,
  "unit_cost": 13.50,
  "selling_price": 16.00,
  "is_vat_exempt": 1,
  "is_active": 1
}

### Update Product (PATCH)
PATCH {{baseURL}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>
Content-Type: application/json

{
    "selling_price": 17.00
}

### Deactivate Product
DELETE {{baseURL}}/products/1
Authorization: Bearer <token>